{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one lady died before the war, which was great.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- And then, I see little objects being thrown in the air, and-- and they were shooting at them and they were blown to pieces.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- and then, I'm observing closer and I see that these little-- that those were little babies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were taking babies from-- from young mothers and throwing them in the air and they were using them for target practice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were throwing them against the brick walls from the homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Their little skulls split in two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Our little infants, our sweetness of life and joy, they were just like-- like-- I-- I don't think I could step on a bug as freely as what they did to our-- to our children.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I don't know if I could step on a bug as freely, I swear to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here, my sister was pregnant, and we have to worry that she should not be noticed by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, we did come home to our hometown, [? burg ?] Chrzanow, and the-- the town had been turned into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I already saw people from different parts of the country, like from Katowice and Ciezkowice and the Bedzin, you know, surrounding towns.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They already were brought to our town, Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they did this with a reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to have the Jews in one place, you know, and this way, they were easy-- it was easier for transportation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rather than to go to each town, they had them together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- we were together in this-- my-- my apartment, as little as it was for us eight people, I think that there were about 25 people in this one apartment.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our apartment, 25 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
